'''Lakshmi Girls Hindu College''' is a girls school located in [[Trinidad and Tobago]]. 

There are about 800-850 students attending Lakshmi Girls and this school is known as the best Business School Of Business studies in the Caribbean. This school is part of the Maha Saba Board of Trinidad and Tobago.

